and we got full of dark ♪

39:54.080 --> 39:58.790
♪ We can hide away our problems
till the winter starts ♪

40:01.330 --> 40:05.710
♪ We pull our walls
and we build them up again ♪

40:06.830 --> 40:10.250
♪ We don't think
they come between us ♪

40:10.250 --> 40:12.830
♪ But we're doing it again ♪

40:15.420 --> 40:19.250
♪ Yeah, we're doing it again ♪

40:19.250 --> 40:23.420
♪ Will we ever find a home
