40:23.420 --> 40:27.420
♪ Yeah, we're doing it again ♪

40:27.420 --> 40:31.210
♪ Will we ever find a home
out there? ♪

40:32.040 --> 40:36.080
♪ Ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh ♪

40:36.080 --> 40:39.120
[ Indistinct conversations ]

40:42.750 --> 40:45.420
You should do it.

40:45.420 --> 40:48.000
♪ Trans-Atlantic trails ♪
Andiamo. Pizza is served.

40:48.000 --> 40:50.290
♪ Coming home to the sky ♪

40:50.290 --> 40:53.170
-To Jon.
-To Jon.

40:53.170 --> 40:54.620
♪ Do you think you'll find ♪
But why the hell
are we toasting him?

40:54.620 --> 40:56.580
♪ Your happiness
there next to mine? ♪
He's still at work.

40:56.580 --> 40:58.670
[ Chuckles ]

40:58.670 --> 41:05.120
