41:05.120 --> 41:07.120
Um, Grandpa, Dad --

41:07.120 --> 41:09.750
Soph, it's okay.

41:09.750 --> 41:12.790
Dad, tell the story
of how Jon and I met.

41:14.210 --> 41:16.620
Oh! Oh.

41:16.620 --> 41:19.210
It all started
in an airport.

41:19.210 --> 41:21.040
Uh, he was on
his way to L.A.,

41:21.040 --> 41:22.250
and she was on her way
to France.

41:22.250 --> 41:25.120
♪ Yeah, we're doing it again ♪

41:25.120 --> 41:29.250
♪ Will we ever find a home
out there? ♪

